{"tid":2264000,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE-Sana自曝曾在舞台上嘔吐？","createTime":"2020-10-30T09:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T15:08:43.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"412bb6f133514e0a8731d69cbb834163695cf09b","tid":2264000,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/10/30/550_1550321_1603994420.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F10%2F30%2F550_1550321_1603994420.webp&h=f59310c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日，人氣組合TWICE成員Sana在節目中表示，她曾經在直播舞台上吐過，讓人大吃一驚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9fEuwA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9fEuwA.jpg&h=c39a4eee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n28日，TWICE成員娜璉、Momo、Sana、志效、Mina、多賢、彩瑛、子瑜出演了於MBC電視台播出的《Radio Star》，拍攝了「TWICE Star」特輯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hM8VtPBk2EhdrDThmrx5tQFFbEXhYYQEUDztDFChjTCMUPVITX25YeUheHiQUOlVJAmtfckcNCSZOOVYWVmlY/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hM8VtPBk2EhdrDThmrx5tQFFbEXhYYQEUDztDFChjTCMUPVITX25YeUheHiQUOlVJAmtfckcNCSZOOVYWVmlY%2Fw644&h=9ffcf051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在當天的節目中，Sana被問到上台前一定會做的步驟。對此,Sana表示：「我們一般都是吃完紫菜包飯再上舞台，但是有次在跳火車舞的時候非常疲憊，而且消化不好，所以就吐了出來。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主持人驚訝地問：「（吐的）是酸水吧？」Sana說：「那次是直播，是真的吐了。跳完舞該起來了，苦惱着怎麼辦，便馬上嚥了下去。」<br />\n<br />\n因此，從那次以後產生了心理陰影的Sana表示：「最近上舞台之前都不吃紫菜包飯了。」<br />\n<br />\n對於Sana專業的反應，主持人金九拉表示：「這對普通人來說真的不是容易的事。」"},{"pid":"e99371296843a277f799a7ea93841e73e42ba82e","tid":2264000,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"想食SANA嘔吐物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527432ec49cd121e066f78c865f8cc8947eaa789","tid":2264000,"uid":60256,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:56:23.000Z","msg":"孕吐？"},{"pid":"675